00:16:13.930 --> 00:16:20.520
death, and a record 17% of Brits said that the monarchy should be abolished.

00:16:21.304 --> 00:16:28.159
Yes, 17% isn’t that much, but just three and a half years before, partly out of

00:16:28.159 --> 00:16:33.979
sympathy for the queen’s terrible year, only 9% of people wanted to abolish it.

00:16:35.279 --> 00:16:41.329
More recently, as you may be aware, her grandson Harry and his wife, Meghan Markle,

00:16:41.619 --> 00:16:47.219
decided that they would remove themselves from the British monarchy, and did several high

00:16:47.229 --> 00:16:53.859
profile interviews directly and indirectly criticising senior members of the royal family.

00:16:54.919 --> 00:17:00.909
